tle>俄罗斯总统拉夫罗夫表示在台湾和其他问题上与中国站在一起</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-lavrov-says-stands-alongside-china-taiwan-other-issues-2024-10-03/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部长在周四发表的采访中表示，俄罗斯在亚洲问题上与中国站在一起，包括批评美国扩大影响力和“蓄意试图”激化台湾周边局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 01:24:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-lavrov-says-stands-alongside-china-taiwan-other-issues-2024-10-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本首相“不恰当”的利率评论令日元感到不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>报告称，俄罗斯、伊朗、中国预计将利用人工智能试图影响美国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-iran-china-expected-use-ai-try-influence-us-election-report-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>根据周三发布的美国年度威胁评估，美国认为俄罗斯、伊朗和中国试图影响 11 月 5 日选举的威胁越来越大，包括利用人工智能传播虚假或分裂性信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-iran-china-expected-use-ai-try-influence-us-election-report-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>解说：伊朗主要核设施长期处于以色列的视线之中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-main-nuclear-facilities-long-israels-sights-2024-10-02/</link><description>周二伊朗对以色列发动导弹袭击后，有人猜测以色列可能会像其长期以来威胁的那样袭击伊朗的核设施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 17:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-main-nuclear-facilities-long-israels-sights-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局将在线招募线人扩大到中国、伊朗和朝鲜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/cia-expands-online-recruitment-informants-china-iran-north-korea-2024-10-02/</link><description>美国中央情报局周三启动了一项新的行动，在中国、伊朗和朝鲜招募线人，这在其所称的招募俄罗斯人的成功努力的基础上又进一步加强了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 16:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/cia-expands-online-recruitment-informants-china-iran-north-korea-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>越南抗议中国军队在争议海域袭击渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-protests-chinese-forces-attack-fishermen-contested-waters-2024-10-02/</link><description>越南周三向中国提出抗议，称三天前一艘越南渔船在有争议的南中国海海域遭到袭击，造成数名渔民受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-protests-chinese-forces-attack-fishermen-contested-waters-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯CEO：打破中国“信心危机”最重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰首席执行官奥拉·康林松表示，结束中国消费者信心危机是梅赛德斯-奔驰中短期内最重要的事情，并将汽车市场描述为一场“达尔文之战”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:19:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车：我们来欧洲是为了带来技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车董事会副主席兼联席总裁布莱恩·顾表示，该汽车制造商不打算在欧洲销售其汽车以提供廉价替代品，而是为了带来自己的技术。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:12:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将拨款高达 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在半导体材料中的应用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</link><description>美国商务部周三表示，计划拨款 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在开发新型可持续半导体材料中的应用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯反击击败卫冕冠军辛纳夺得中国公开赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</link><description>卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯在周三的中国公开赛决赛中，在先失一盘的情况下奋起直追，在决定性的抢七中顽强拼搏，以 6-7(6) 6-4 7-6(3) 击败卫冕冠军詹尼克·辛纳，夺得个人第四个网球冠军。季节。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>马里诺队击败蔚山队，使亚冠联赛重回正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</link><description>横滨水手队周三从首日耻辱中恢复过来，在日本以 4-0 击败韩国蔚山 HD，让他们的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛重回正轨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>